成年家養的[[水牛|水牛]]只重300-600公斤，在野外的雌性河水牛重800公斤，雄牛重1200公斤。河水牛肩高1.8米，體長2.9米。在[[印度|印度]][[阿薩姆邦|阿薩姆邦]]的種群棲息在[[喜瑪拉雅山|喜瑪拉雅山]]山腳的[[森林|森林]]，體型且較為大，平均重900公斤，雄牛較雌牛大些許，肩高1.7米，可達2米高。最純種的河水牛棲息在印度的[[加濟蘭加國家公園|加濟蘭加國家公園]]及不丹[[馬納斯國家公園|馬納斯國家公園]]。牠們也分佈在[[緬甸|緬甸]]西北部。

== 基因污染 ==
河水牛受到[[基因污染|基因污染]]的威脅。家養的[[水牛|水牛]]日間在[[森林|森林]]內放牧，與河水牛有所接觸<ref name="animalinfo.org" /><ref>{{cite web |url=http://wildlifetrustofindia.org/news-archives/2006/02/15/wild-buffalo-faces-extinction/ |title=Wild buffalo faces extinction |date=February 15, 2006 |publisher=Wildlife Trust of India |accessdate=2009-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120119141720/http://wildlifetrustofindia.org/news-archives/2006/02/15/wild-buffalo-faces-extinction/ |archive-date=2012-01-19 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.wildcattleconservation.org/WildCattleNews/wildcattlenews06.html#news20060215 |title=Wild buffalo faces extinction |publisher=Wild Cattle Conservation Project |date=February 15, 2006 |accessdate=2009-02-02 |archive-date=2009-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090202125814/http://www.wildcattleconservation.org/WildCattleNews/wildcattlenews06.html#news20060215 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hindu.com/2006/02/26/stories/2006022601090900.htm |title=Project to conserve wild Asian buffalo |last=Perappadan |first=Bindu Shajan |publisher=The Hindu |date=Feb 26, 2006 |accessdate=2009-02-02 |archive-date=2009-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090204224126/http://www.hindu.com/2006/02/26/stories/2006022601090900.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://southasia.oneworld.net/article/view/129014/1/8674 |title=Project to conserve wild Asian buffalo |last=Perappadan |first=Bindu Shajan |date=March 8, 2006 |publisher=OneWorld |accessdate=2009-02-02 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100813094406/http://southasia.oneworld.net/article/view/129014/1/8674 |archivedate=2010年8月13日 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.wii.gov.in/envis/ungulatesofindia/northeast.htm |title=Asian Wild Buffalo (Bubalus bubalis Linnaeus, 1758) |coauthors=P.K.Mathur, P.K. Malik and P.D. Muley |date=July 13, 2007 |work=Wildlife Institute of India |accessdate=2009-02-02 |archive-date=2009-01-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090108031936/http://www.wii.gov.in/envis/ungulatesofindia/northeast.htm |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，發生種間[[繁殖|繁殖]]。種間繁殖令河水牛的血統受到污染，相信是源自於[[南亞|南亞]]。除了在[[印度|印度]]以外，純種的河水牛就只有在[[泰國|泰國]]可以見到，但數量只有約50頭，而在沿[[越南|越南]]、[[老撾|老撾]]及[[柬埔寨|柬埔寨]]邊界的[[安南山脈|安南山脈]]也可以見到。現時在[[亞洲|亞洲]]其他地方的河水牛都並非純種的河水牛，且也有被引進到[[阿根廷|阿根廷]]及[[玻利維亞|玻利維亞]]。

